<mxfile host="app.diagrams.net">
  <diagram id="uedDBjp-Z_iSIwonFi2j" name="Page-1">
    <mxGraphModel dx="4482" dy="3754" grid="1" gridSize="10" guides="1" tooltips="1" connect="1" arrows="1" fold="1" page="1" pageScale="1" pageWidth="1654" pageHeight="2336" math="0" shadow="0">
      <root>
        <mxCell id="0" />
        <mxCell id="1" parent="0" />
        <UserObject label="" plantUmlData="{&quot;data&quot;:&quot;@startuml\ntitle Hospital Management System\n\n&#39; --- Base Classes ---\nclass User {\n    +userId: Long\n    +username: String\n    +password: String\n    +email: String\n    +phone: String\n    +role: String\n    +auth: Boolean\n    +isFrozen: Boolean\n    +permissions: Set&lt;String&gt;\n    +login()\n    +signup()\n    +logout()\n}\n\nclass Patient {\n    +id: Long\n    +history: historyD\n    +viewDoctorDetails()\n    +listDoctors()\n    +makeAppointment()\n    +rate()\n    +viewHistory()\n    +makeHistory()\n}\n\nclass Doctor {\n    +id: Long\n    +specialization: String\n    +rating: Float\n    +bio: String\n    +certificates: List&lt;String&gt;\n    +updateBio()\n    +reviewPatientHistory()\n    +listAppointment()\n    +makeAvailableTime()\n    +canManageSchedule(): Boolean\n}\n\nclass Admin {\n    +deleteUser()\n    +verifyDoctor()\n    +freezeAccount()\n    +unfreezeUser()\n    +listUsers()\n    +listDoctorsWantVerify()\n}\n\n&#39; --- Data Entities ---\nclass historyD {\n    +id: Long\n    +history: String\n    +note: String\n}\n\nclass Appointment {\n    +id: Long\n    +availabilitySlot: Long\n    +note: String\n    +patientName: String\n    +doctorName: String\n    +patientId: Long\n    +doctorId: Long\n    +date: Date\n    +timeSlot: String\n    +phoneNumber: String\n}\n\n\nclass AvailabilitySlot {\n    +id: Long\n    +days: List&lt;String&gt;\n    +startTime: Time\n    +endTime: Time\n    +durationMinutes: Integer\n}\n\nclass AppointedPatient {\n    +id: Long\n    +patientUserId: Long\n    +patientName: String\n}\n\n&#39; --- OCL Invariants (Formalized) ---\nnote left of User\n  **Account Integrity Rules:**\n  context User inv IdentityValidation:\n    User.allInstances()-&gt;isUnique(email) and self.username.size() &gt; 0\n\n  context User inv FrozenAccountRestriction:\n    self.isFrozen = true implies self.permissions-&gt;isEmpty()\nend note\n\nnote right of Doctor\n  **Clinical Standards:**\n  context Doctor inv MandatoryCredentials:\n    self.certificates-&gt;notEmpty()\n\n  context Doctor inv VerifiedAccessOnly:\n    self.auth = true implies self.canManageSchedule()\nend note\n\nnote bottom of Appointment\n  **Scheduling Logic:**\n  context Appointment inv PreventDoubleBooking:\n    Appointment.allInstances()-&gt;isUnique(availabilitySlot)\n\n  context Appointment inv PatientIdentityRequired:\n    self.patientId &lt;&gt; null\nend note\n\n\n&#39; --- Associations &amp; Multiplicities ---\nUser &lt;|-- Patient\nUser &lt;|-- Doctor\nUser &lt;|-- Admin\n\nPatient \&quot;1\&quot; *-- \&quot;1\&quot; historyD : owned by\nDoctor \&quot;1\&quot; -- \&quot;*\&quot; AvailabilitySlot : schedules\nAppointment \&quot;*\&quot; -- \&quot;1\&quot; AvailabilitySlot : reserves\nDoctor \&quot;1\&quot; -- \&quot;*\&quot; AppointedPatient : sees\nPatient \&quot;1\&quot; -- \&quot;*\&quot; Appointment : books\nDoctor \&quot;1\&quot; -- \&quot;*\&quot; Appointment : attends\n\n@enduml\n&quot;,&quot;format&quot;:&quot;svg&quot;}" id="OyADFi8Tq_fXoBviTkyV-115">
          <mxCell parent="1" style="shape=image;noLabel=1;verticalAlign=top;aspect=fixed;imageAspect=0;image=data:image/svg+xml,;" vertex="1">
            <mxGeometry height="1007" width="1064" x="-1630" y="-2270" as="geometry" />
          </mxCell>
        </UserObject>
      </root>
